      "comment": "BOWIE SUNNY (2) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 22.93 with a 2 length win at Warragul over 400m. Will go close again if runs up to latest. ROWDY'S BEAST (1) missed the frame latest when sixth at The Meadows (31.06) but scored three back at Shepparton (25.54). Has ability and a bold showing is expected. SPECIAL LAD (6) broke a string of placings finishing in the money four on end before a last start fourth (22.72) at Geelong. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from four starts. Should be about the money. DR. PATRICK (7) is a last start winner who rates one of the chances again.",
